<H3> <TI>   28th Joint MIA Search Concludes </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  BK2403154194 Hanoi VNA in English 1514 GMT 24 Mar 94 </F>
<F P=103> BK2403154194 </F>
<F P=104>  Hanoi VNA </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Hanoi VNA March 24 -- The 28th joint search for the 
American servicemen missing in action (MIA) during the war was 
conducted from Fb. 26 to March 22 in various provinces and 
cities in Vietnam. The US-Vietnamese joint teams have got a lot 
of information about MIAs and a considerable number of sets of 
US servicemens remains. The US side thanked and highly valued 
Vietnam's effective cooperation in this humanitarian issues. 

</TEXT>

