headline] 
  [Text] Pyongyang, March 25 (KCNA) -- The U.S. imperialists 
staged a provocative electronic aerial warfare exercise directed 
against the North of Korea in the air above the Oeyon islet, 
South Korea, in the daytime of March 23 with the mobilization of 
more than 200 warplanes of various types, according to military 
sources. 
  They also staged a war exercise in the air above Kapyong, 
Uijongbu, Yoju, Kunwi and Tanyang that night till early next 
morning with sorties of more than 300 fighter planes of various 
types. 
