aerial photographing and electronic reconnaissance on the 
strategic interior and all other areas of the North. 
  Formations of helicopter gunships belonging to the South 
Korean puppet army which were sent to support the ground attack 
operation in Paju County staged a missile strike exercise, while 
formations of transport helicopters flew over Yonchon County and 
Chorwon County, South Korean Kangwon Province, for an airlifting 
operation. 
  Meanwhile, formations of large transport planes carrying 
many 
aggression troops and death tools flew to the U.S. Airforce 
bases in Osan and Kunsan from their overseas bases. The 
airlifted combat equipment was deployed in operational areas. 
  The war gambles of the U.S. imperialists and the South 
Korean 
puppets which are getting more reckless with each passing day 
are driving the situation of the Korean peninsula to the brink 
of war. 

