<F P=104>  Hanoi VNA </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Hanoi VNA March 24 -- Cuban Foreign Minister Roberto 
Robaina Gonzales and his party left Ho Chi Minh City this 
afternoon, ending his 4-day official friendship to Vietnam. 
  Mr R.R. Gonzales was cordially received last night by Vo 
Tran 
Chi, secretary of Ho Chi Minh City party committee, who informed 
him of the city's socio-economic situation in recent years, and 
Truong Tan Sang, mayor of the city. 
  While in Vietnam, Mr Gonzales and his party paid a floral 
