<H3> <TI>   Mahathir Departs for New Delhi G-15 Meeting </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  BK2703092594 Kuala Lumpur Voice of Malaysia in English 0600 
GMT 27 Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> BK2703092594 </F>
<F P=104>  Kuala Lumpur Voice of Malaysia </F>


