<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105>Tagalog </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] President Ramos said today that there is no need to 
send Philippine combat troops to Korea in view of the threat of 
war there. According to the president, there is no need to 
panic, and he gave assurances that the Department of Foreign 
