  The Japanese reactionaries' false propaganda and pressure 
campaign against the DPRK are dangerous acts aggravating the 
tensions on the Korean peninsula and bringing the situation to a 
more acute phase. 
  In crying over "threat" from the DPRK, they intend to invent 
a pretext to justify their armament expansion and Japan's 
