isolate and stifle the North when he prattled again about 
"effectiveness of pressure" by the "international cooperation 
system". 
  Facts clearly show that the Kim Yong-sam group is, indeed, a 
never-to-be-condoned group of traitors who do not want either 
North- South dialogue or peace and peaceful reunification of the 
